# retain

**Instance Property**

The callback used to retain each value as they are added to the collection. If `NULL`, values are not retained. See [doc://com.apple.corefoundation/documentation/CoreFoundation/CFSetRetainCallBack] for a descriptions of this function’s parameters.

## Declaration

```swift
var retain: CFSetRetainCallBack!
```
